====Usage notes====
This may be the only kanji with a six-{{l|en|mora}} reading, of ''uketamawari''. However, this reading is more often spelled with the final ''-ri'' spelled in kana (as {{m|ja|承り}}; [[okurigana]]) to clarify and disambiguate the reading of the single kanji.

This kanji is also one of very few kanji with five-{{l|en|mora}} readings, and the only verb, namely {{m|ja|承る|tr=uketamawaru|pos=with the kanji comprising the five-mora ''uketamawa-'' part}}.

